event.title: FSFE booth at FrOSCon conference in St. Augustin, Germany

body.p: On August 22/23 there is FrOSCon, a Free Software conference, at the Bonn-Rhein-Sieg University of Applied Science in 53757 Sankt Augustin. FSFE will be present during FrOSCon with a booth. If you have any questions or like to meet the people behind the Free Software Foundation Europe.
